name: Met Eye ball Coffin
description:
This comes in three different colors for the fill area.   Dark Red, Black , And Dark Green. 
Its easy to apply. Just peel and  place on the coffin insert  in the Met Pro. 
The lock lights show through perfectly and now you know how many Balls you have locked by how many red eyes are glowing. 
   Printed on sturdy clear vinyl and cut to the perfect shape of the coffin.

name: BSD UGLY VAMP MOD
description:
Ok so you can finally put that week end at Bernie's crappy vamp in the coffin to rest.  
The new Ugly Vamp mod actually shows the lights lighting in the coffin!! He actually lights up...
   Keep in mind that this is  rubber and  though pliable the paint will eventual peal if bended excessively. I also recommend replacing the original bulbs with LEDs for heat sake.
